UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Rheanna,$B$BImagine my surprise at the postman\'s refusal to take my letter to thee! Surely, this is a mistake? Mine eyes scour over the meticulous copies I\'ve made of each of my past letters, but I can find no cause for errant worry. I shall deliver this letter by hand if the damned fool is convinced that my love of loves would refuse my correspondence!$B' WHERE word_id = 126394;
UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Rheanna,$B$BImagine my surprise at the postman\'s refusal to take my letter to thee! Surely, this is a mistake? Mine eyes scour over the meticulous copies I\'ve made of each of my past letters, but I can find no cause for errant worry. I shall deliver this letter by hand if the damned fool is convinced that my love of loves would refuse my correspondence!$B' WHERE word_id = 126394;
