UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Dalaran Dining Guide$BWhen Inzi Charmlight opened A Hero\'s Welcome shortly after the city relocated, locals and visitors alike lined up to lay their weapons down and sink their teeth into a tough hunk of bread!  Seating is ample, prices are fair and the full bar offers indulgences from all over the world to help you feel satisfyingly heroic.  No matter what you order, save room for the Mead-Basted Caribou!$B' WHERE word_id = 126957;
