UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Q: My co-workers all seem to be doing more damage than I do.  How can I catch up with them without looking like a dufus?$BA: It\'s not all about damage.  You can aid your group in other ways - Arcane Refreshment spells are a good example.  If that doesn\'t pan out, perhaps a career in the arcane arts isn\'t the right career path for you.  We hear that hunting is easy!
