UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Entry 205) Most of the Alliance forces have left for Azeroth.  Hopefully the carefully-compiled reports that we sent with General Turalyon will make it back to Dalaran safely.$BNer\'zhul\'s reckless portals have torn Farahlon apart, its green hills now quickly crumbling as the Twisting Nether corrupts the earth.  I have to find a passage back to the place I was before!$B' WHERE word_id = 126941;
