                -ARCHAVON$B' WHERE word_id = 126466;
UPDATE trans_words SET content_loc3='Day 214701:
My brothers are back!  It turns out they were sleeping in other closed off halls.$BI\'m a little mad that they left me alone to do all the watching, but I shared my shinier baubles with them anyway because I\'m tired of being alone and attacked all the time.
                -ARCHAVON$BDay 214760:
